The paper deals with specifying a transaction controller for concurrent programs, which is a topic related to programming languages (cs.PL), distributed computing (cs.DC), and data structures (cs.DS). The paper also discusses the correctness property of concurrent runs under the transaction controller, which is related to software engineering (cs.SE) and logic in computer science (cs.LO).
